ELECTRICAL ENGINEER: Designing and building electrical systems

Category: Electrical
Base skill: 30% (+5%/level, cap 98%)

Designing, building, and wiring electrical systems and circuitry from
scratch, not just fixing what already exists. The skill of the person
who builds the device, as opposed to the technician who repairs one
someone else built.

NOTES:
  No AetherMUD command currently rolls this skill directly. It is
  available for character concept and staff-adjudicated roleplay.

SEE ALSO: skills, computer repair, robot electronics, mechanical engineer
